compose_with_a_grid_activity::howto_card: Gaditti kan jiru kaardii muraati. Kaameeraa jalqabsiisiuu fi suuraa kaasuuf "Qabadhu" kan jedhu filadhu.
compose_with_a_grid_activity::preview_ca: Yoo danda'ame fayyadama kaameeraa bilbilakeerraa amala tarsaa bani.
compose_with_a_grid_activity::text_card_: Amma erga waa'ee tarsaa fayyadamuu barannee, yerichi kan shaakalaati.
compose_with_a_grid_activity::title: Hojii Tarsaatiin Qopheessi
compose_with_a_grid_activity::clip_card_: Goodaayyicha guutuudhaan sararaa fi walitti dhufeenyasaa qophiikee keessatti fayyadami.
